That land administration agent who started the lawsuit organized a business dinner and invited the co-owners of our land.
He attemped to drag more people to his side.
But within 33 co-owners there were only 3 who attended the dinner.
These are people who have debt or land loan.
The gamblers make quick friend with con-men.

The mass majority of our society don't know or did not study in this area and yet they created most of of the value for the society.
It still irritates me that those who major in law always side with thieves and robbers.
Together, they steal money and land from those who have benefitted the society.

The law have many jargo and special structure.
It's too difficult for ordinary people to understand.
To make the situation worse, those fraudulant legislators had corrupted the law and made thousands of holes in it.
The lawsuits like our case are actually caused by such "holes".
These thieves and robbers already made billions of dollars from it.

The hand-cranked generator MKIV is done.
Greasing the gears did improve the rotation.
But still, the resistance/friction inside the system was too big.
To solve the problem, I created MKV with similar design but replaced planetary gears with spur gears.
I even lowered the gear ratio to 1:4.
The generator will still be 550 DC motor.
I'll make a model that really works. And then keep modifying it.
After condidering for 9 months, now I have more complete scheme for CAFit.
It will be a power/water plant with a skin of a gym which is capable of helding Marathon events.
The slogan of this project is "Workout to have a cleaner sky".
The main power source will not be human power, but the solar energy  collected by stirling engine and wind power collected by wind pumps.

